            "stanza_text": "Quand tu me lis une histoire\nEmpruntée aux « Faits Divers »,\nJe me refuse à la croire –\nLe monde est-il si pervers ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Les gens sont-ils si sublimes ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "(J’en conviens, moins fréquemment)",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Tu lis ou plutôt tu limes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Et ce m’est un agrément",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Les gens sont-ils si sublimes ?\n(J’en conviens, moins fréquemment)\nTu lis ou plutôt tu limes\nEt ce m’est un agrément"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Alors qu’à mon tour je lime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "En travail d’un vers subtil,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "D’ouïr, marquant mètre et rime,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Ce martellement gentil,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Alors qu’à mon tour je lime,\nEn travail d’un vers subtil,\nD’ouïr, marquant mètre et rime,\nCe martellement gentil,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Et puis encor ce que j’aime",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Dans ces récits fabuleux",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "C’est d’être fabuleux même,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Contes noirs ou contes bleus.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Et puis encor ce que j’aime\nDans ces récits fabuleux\nC’est d’être fabuleux même,\nContes noirs ou contes bleus."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "C’est ainsi que sous la lampe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Passent les heures du soir…",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "La nuit s’est faite : je rampe",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Me coucher, las de m’asseoir.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "7",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "C’est ainsi que sous la lampe\nPassent les heures du soir…\nLa nuit s’est faite : je rampe\nMe coucher, las de m’asseoir."
        }
